pierced him a maximum of 4 times. He feared me...Then ran up and snare DOTed me....Then following th Dot was a Harms Touch...While still feared he Poisoned DOTed me and then waved goodbye and sat down. Just wondering if anyone can tell me what to do the next time a duel a deathknight !<br>
